rows.name:
...So that's how it is. It seems
our paths continue to entwine.

rows.label: bf06140195_0030
rows.name:
To be honest, I was really hoping there
was some way you could stick around.

rows.label: bf06140195_0040
rows.name:
I was just thinking of
asking you myself.

rows.label: bf06140195_0050
rows.name: Saved you the trouble, did I?
